Good morning. When I run step 1 of end-to-end,js test (which is the enrolment of user admin) I get:

```2017/01/17 12:57:17 http: TLS handshake error from 127.0.0.1:36424: tls: oversized record received with length 21536```

Am I doing something wrong?

I'm running with the latest level of code ( I've cloned again all the repos less than one hour ago). It used to work with the level of code I had installed about 10 days ago.
<@U1GPHH6PQ> COP now starts by default with TLS enabled, you need to disable it by modifying the “tls_disable: true” in testconfig.json
<@U1L2C9F3R> can you review this change for more accurate test coverage numbers: <http://gerrit.hyperledger.org/r/4083>
Eventhub support is in gerrit for early review (<https://gerrit.hyperledger.org/r/#/c/4093/1>)
